title: CCK Podcast: The Worst Video on The Internet (with Josh Wolf, Ria & Ellie)
description:
Josh Wolf sent KFC a truly disgusting video, he calls in to discuss how he pulled the prank off. Nobody can explain why they hate Logan Paul. Who would die first if Trent and Robbie both got Coronavirus?
